Package com.project.springbootjavafx.models

package com.project.springbootjavafx.models
  • Class
    Description
    Ceny
    The Ceny class represents the pricing information for a specific trip type.
    Hotele
    The Hotele class represents a hotel entity in the system.
    Klienci
    The Klienci class represents a client in the system.
    ListaNocyHoteli
    The ListaNocyHoteli class represents an immutable view of hotel night list data.
    ListyHoteli
    The ListyHoteli class represents a hotel list entry that associates a room, a city for the trip night, and a hotel.
    ListyHoteliKey
    The ListyHoteliKey class represents a composite primary key for the ListyHoteli entity.
    Miasta
    The Miasta class represents a city entity in the system.
    MiastaWycieczek
    The MiastaWycieczek class represents an association between a trip type and a city for a specific night of a trip.
    Models
    The Models interface serves as a common contract for all model classes within the application.
    Pokoje
    The Pokoje class represents a room entity in the system.
    TypyWycieczek
    The TypyWycieczek class represents a type of trip in the system.
    Wycieczki
    The Wycieczki class represents a trip in the system.
